            "properties": {
                "description": "Işık 2021 clarifies the location of Aği = Hagi (renamed Kocapınar by Turkish authorities in 1959 according to Geonames), which lies northwest of Erciş, rather than some other locations east of Erciş that are commonly confused with it in the literature.",
                "link": "https://pleiades.stoa.org/places/742516213/geonames-location-modern-kocapinar",
